Karana chapter</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uplangstrump.showPublicProfile?language=EN>P Langstrump</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Least Equipped 55th Level Druid</span><br> <font color=#8E9173>(5/20/01 8:20:47 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.interlog.com/~wings/jane/a_lindgren/lindgren_pics/pippi.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Other dragons</span><hr size=1> *grins* no, CoG is not in rotation for other dragons at this point.  Hope it's ok I am answering for Lag here <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  it will always be the raid organizer's decision whether they feel it's appropriate or not, but hey, they just started organizing naggy and vox raids... <p><HR>
